Package de.dbis.services

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Configuration
    Configures the machine to work as a Master or Slave.
    DisplayVideos
    Retrieves the list of Videos from the server for a specific category for the logged in user.
    FileUpload
    Uploads the File to server.
    GetProperty
    Read and returns the configurations from .properties files.
    Java2MySql
    Establishes connection to the MySql database.
    ObjectStore
    Uploads the given File to i5 cloud object store.
    OIDCLoginStart
    Initializes OpenID Connect login procedure.
    OIDCTokens
    Get Access Tokens for Open ID connect login.
    OIDCVerifyAccessToken
    Verifies the Access Token for validity.
    RabbitMQReceive
    Receives the notification from slave nodes through RabbitMQ server once the video is uploaded.
    RabbitMQSend
    Sends the video to the RabbitMQ server for transcoding.
    Thumbnail
    Generates Thumbnails for the given Video
    VideoDetails
    Returns video information and status.
    VideoInfo
    Returns the video codec of the input file
